                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 3691/87.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Combs</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Guatemala</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1907-02-22">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 22, 1907</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Reports that the minister for foreign affairs of Honduras telegraphs that
                    Nicaragua, by its invasion of Honduras, has terminated pending negotiations for
                    pacific settlement.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
